| **2** | SFPM accumulator adapter live. ct0 reads growthInside for a single configured range. | Options on asset0/V_B_shares accrue streaming premium from Angstrom rewards. Short put on a range earns theta. Long put pays for protection. This is the minimum viable product for theta trading. |
